*TITR
simple file with sag parameter for LGC API testing
*OLOC
*APRI
*CONSI
*PREC 6
*INSTR
*FRAME testFrame 0 0 0 0 0 0 1
*POIN
left 	0 -1 0	%SX 1 SY 1 SZ 1
middle 	0 0 0	%SX 1 SY 1 SZ 1
right 	0 1 0	%SX 1 SY 1 SZ 1
P1 0 0 0
P2 0 1 0
*ENDFRAME
% observations are chosen such that VS=0.001, VC=0.002, RS=0.003, RC=0.004 (units sag:meter, curvature:unitless)
*OBSXYZ
left 	0.007 -1 0.003	1 1 0.1234 ID leftObs
middle 	0.003 0  0.001	1 1 0.1234 ID middleObs
right 	0.007 1  0.003	1 1 0.1234 ID rightObs
*SAGCONNECT sag1 testFrame 0 0 0 0 VS VC  RS RC %RC %Vert Sag, Vert curbature, Rad Sag, Rad curbature
%*SAGCONNECT sag1 testFrame 0 0 0 0 VC  RS RC %RC %Vert Sag, Vert curbature, Rad Sag, Rad curbature
left
middle
right
% this sag element is fixed. it determines the position of the points
*SAGCONNECT sag2 testFrame 0 0 0 0
P1
P2
*END

